body:
Controversial typing?

So I realised Taylor swift is actually an istp, with some help from my entj friend/sister 😂

It defs explain why some people believe she’s just paranoid and has a victim mentality and others don’t… Tertiary Ni can be like that. It also explains why she can be kind of over sensitive at times (Inferior Fe).

Might also explain why she’s so edgy now 😂

cause you’re giving it away like extra change 
hoping it’ll end up in his pocket...

cause you’re giving it away like extra change

hoping it’ll end up in his pocket

but he leaves you out like a penny in the rain

cause it’s not his price to pay, not his price to pay
